Euro Leaflet

Got European shape file and add some random number. Try popup by clicking on country.

europe_countries <- getEuropeCountries()
value <- sample(x = seq(0,3,by = 0.1), size = length(europe_countries),
                replace = TRUE)
europe_countries$value <- value

pal <- colorQuantile("Greens", NULL, n = 5)

polygon_popup <- paste0("<strong>Name: </strong>", europe_countries$name, "<br>",
                        "<strong>Indicator: </strong>", round(europe_countries$value,2))

map = leaflet() %>% 
      addProviderTiles("CartoDB.Positron") %>% 
      setView(48.5141, 8.3944,
              zoom = 1) %>% 
      addPolygons(data = europe_countries, 
                  fillColor= ~pal(value),
                  fillOpacity = 0.4, 
                  weight = 2, 
                  color = "white",
                  popup = polygon_popup)
map
